<br>
/afk I am at location neg 600 by pos 100, check my low price on raw silk armor!<br>
<br>
Then all you need to do is send them a tell to know where to find them.<br>
<br>
Also please remove anonymous, so /who vendor name gives a description of what we are looking for. If I know the vendor is a Ogre warrior then I won't look at all the gnomes around it.<br>
<br>
I hope those 2 ideas can make things a bit easier on everyone, if you think it's a good move please tell others.<br>
<br>
